definition: unlikely to go so far as to/not as bad as

sentences.english: Make sure you drink plenty to save-off dehydration .
sentences.chinese: 記得喝多點水纔不至於虛脫。

sentences.english: As the Scripture says, "Anyone who trusts in him will never be put to shame."
sentences.chinese: 經上說，凡信他的人，必不至於羞愧。

sentences.english: And Nathan said unto David, The LORD also hath put away thy sin; thou shalt not die.
sentences.chinese: 拿單說，耶和華已經除掉你的罪，你必不至於死。

sentences.english: Now let me do it a second time to show you that -- I'm saying this poorly.
sentences.chinese: 還不至於如此呢，現在讓我再做一次給你們看。

sentences.english: I should know: For a few months, I was one of the suckers.
sentences.chinese: 如果早知道這些，我就不至於上他們幾個月的當了。

sentences.english: Desdemona. If you say so, I hope you will not kill me.
sentences.chinese: 苔絲狄蒙娜要是您這樣說，我希望您不至於把我殺死。

sentences.english: I am wiser than to believe what you call money talks.
sentences.chinese: 我不至於可笑到相信你所謂的金錢萬能的說法。

sentences.english: Rational fear is good - it stops us getting killed.
sentences.chinese: 合理的憂慮是好的，它讓我們不至於滅亡。

sentences.english: To avoid overfeeding, consider giving your dog low- or reduced-fat dairy products.
sentences.chinese: 爲了不至於餵過量，可以考慮使用低脂奶製品。

sentences.english: I will speak of your statutes before kings and will not be put to shame
sentences.chinese: 我也要在君王面前，論說你的法度，並不至於羞愧。

sentences.english: The kidney is in charge of the bones. Teeth are fixed, not to lose.
sentences.chinese: 腎主骨，牙齒固定，不至於擺動脫落。

sentences.english: All this I have told you so that you will not go astray.
sentences.chinese: 我已將這些事告訴你們，使你們不至於跌倒。

sentences.english: All iniquity is sin. And there is a sin unto death.
sentences.chinese: 任何的不義都是罪過，但也有不至於死的罪過。

sentences.english: Please remember that there is always a light lighting for you !
sentences.chinese: 還是買品牌的燈吧，不至於總爆管，換來換去恨麻煩。

sentences.english: Even if as for is not at a loss for words, also can only be ambiguous at least.
sentences.chinese: 即使不至於張口結舌，至少也只能含含糊糊。

sentences.english: I had a better command of English than to make such foolish mistakes.
sentences.chinese: 我的英語學得很好，不至於犯這樣愚蠢的錯誤。
